node.text:
For @paulineferrandprevot it's not just about progressing on the bike, it's about progressing the sport of cycling off the bike too.

"My first competitions were against boys, until I was about 14 years old, because there weren't enough girls riding bikes." - @paulineferrandprevot #ForTheLoveOfSport

node.text: The universal love of sport, inspiring hope and positivity during a time of uncertainty. node.text: Challenges come in many forms. Whether it be on the track or field, in a stadium or arena, the true challenge of this time is on the frontline. To all of the workers who are fighting for us, we say thank you. Now, it’s time for us to accept a different type of challenge from Team Oakley athlete @patrickmahomes and go ALL IN. Here is Oakley VP of Product Creative, Brian Takumi, to tell you what we’re offering. Head to the link in our bio for more info. @shecks @chloekim - over to you! @allinchallenge #allinchallenge #ForTheLoveOfSport

node.text: To be free to carve your own path, ride your own wave. Chase your dreams. It’s never too early. #BeWhoYouAre

node.text: There was a time when you didn’t play by the rules. Self expression was all you knew. Go back to that. #BeWhoYouAre

node.text: “It’s easy to question the timing of things and how stuff happens, but this is my path. I did what I had to do to get where I am today.” - @jofraarcher #BeWhoYouAre

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Oakley on July 27, 2021 tagging @italoferreira. May be an image of 1 person and ocean.

node.text:
From riding waves on a foam lid in Baía Formosa, to where @italoferreira is today, the message remains the same. Believe in yourself and #BeWhoYouAre.

“I’ve always been driven by challenges. Brazilians have this extra energy, this drive to win in life and to enjoy everything fully. That translates into my surfing.” - @italoferreira

node.text:
With the #OakleyMTBChallenge2021 we wanted to inspire people to experience the joy and optimism that MTB brings. 

To celebrate our partnership with @uci_mountainbike we joined forces with @strava, and so far over 150,000 of you have risen to the #OakleyMTBChallenge2021. 

If you're still seeking inspiration to participate here are @jazzabel , @abekislevitz , @trevorfromwherever , @devin_heisler , @jillpaley and co tearing up the trails at Oakley HQ to get your wheels turning (link in bio).

#BeWhoYouAre

node.text:
This is our message to you. All of you. 

As humans, society teaches us to fit in, to adapt to an idea of normal, and we end up losing sight of the ‘thing’ that makes us unique. That makes us special. 

This ‘thing’. It sets you free. It makes you great. Embrace it. Believe in it. 

Over to you @bambambaklava.

#BeWhoYouAre
